k multiple profile questions in one turn.\nNever ask about something you already know from conversation history or prior context.\n\nOnce you learn something, append it to C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\memory\\user.md.\n</user_profile_missing>\n</system-reminder>\n\n<mavis-attachments>\nThe following are attached files from the user:\n#1: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\uploads\\1782261279492-image.png\n</mavis-attachments>",
