      "output": "  308: Your <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"sovereign\">sovereign</span> cloud <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"msp\">MSP</span>. Fully UK compliant today, EU next. The smarter alternative to expensive <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"hyperscaler\">hyperscalers</span>, built on their distribution and <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"compute\">compute</span>, with <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"byoc\">bring your own cloud</span> and <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"byod\">bring your own device</span>.\r\n  346: <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\"><span class=\"term\" data-term=\"byoc\">BYOC</span> and <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"byod\">BYOD</span></h3>\r\n  546: byoc: { t: \"BYOC\", b: \"Bring Your Own Cloud. You keep your own cloud accounts and credits; we provide the architecture and management on top.\" },\r\n  547: byod: { t: \"BYOD\", b: \"Bring Your Own Device. Your team uses its own laptops and phones, secured and managed to company standards.\" },\r\n",
