      "code": "{\"filePath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\.mavis\\\\sessions\\\\mvs_8d6cdf45af11451ca152d51c37e4fa64\\\\workspace\\\\akcloud-site\\\\index.html\", \"offset\": 325, \"limit\": 80}",
      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.minimax\\sessions\\mvs_8d6cdf45af11451ca152d51c37e4fa64\\workspace\\akcloud-site\\index.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n325:   <div style=\"position:relative; margin-top:30px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12.5px; color:#787878; letter-spacing:0.04em;\">powered by ANDIEKOBBIETECH<span style=\"color:#39FF14;\">.</span></div>\n326: </section>\n327: \n328: <!-- CIRCUIT RULE -->\n329: <div class=\"circuit-rule\"><div class=\"circuit-line\"><div class=\"circuit-pulse\"></div></div></div>\n330: \n331: <!-- THE ALTERNATIVE -->\n332: <section id=\"about\" style=\"position:relative; z-index:1; max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; box-sizing:border-box; padding:96px 40px; scroll-margin-top:88px;\">\n333:   <div class=\"section-eyebrow\">The Sovereign Alternative</div>\n334:   <h2 class=\"section-h2\" style=\"max-width:780px;\">Hyperscaler power. Sovereign control. Without the hyperscaler invoice.</h2>\n335:   <p class=\"section-p\" style=\"max-width:680px;\">AKCloud is a <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"msp\">managed service provider</span> for founders and organisations that want the reach of Azure, AWS and GCP without the runaway bills or the loss of data <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"sovereign\">sovereignty</span>. We run your infrastructure on UK regions, govern it to compliance standards, and let you keep your own cloud accounts and your own devices.</p>\n336:   <div class=\"grid-3\">\n337:     <div class=\"card\">\n338:       <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\">Sovereign by default</h3>\n339:       <p style=\"margin:12px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">Your data stays in UK regions. Fully UK compliant today, with EU residency arriving next. Governance and audit trails built in, not bolted on.</p>\n340:     </div>\n341:     <div class=\"card\">\n342:       <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\">Hyperscaler distribution</h3>\n343:       <p style=\"margin:12px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">We <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"leverage\">leverage</span> the distribution and raw <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"compute\">compute</span> of Azure, AWS and GCP at managed rates, so you get their scale and tooling without paying their full retail price.</p>\n344:     </div>\n345:     <div class=\"card\">\n346:       <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\"><span class=\"term\" data-term=\"byoc\">BYOC</span> and <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"byod\">BYOD</span></h3>\n347:       <p style=\"margin:12px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">Bring your own cloud and bring your own device. Keep your accounts, credits and hardware. We provide the architecture, security and day to day management on top.</p>\n348:     </div>\n349:   </div>\n350: </section>\n351: \n352: <!-- CIRCUIT RULE -->\n353: <div class=\"circuit-rule\"><div class=\"circuit-line\"><div class=\"circuit-pulse\" style=\"animation-delay: -1.5s;\"></div></div></div>\n354: \n355: <!-- CLOUD CREDITS -->\n356: <section id=\"credits\" style=\"position:relative; z-index:1; box-sizing:border-box; padding:96px 0; background:#0c0c0c; border-top:1px solid #242424; border-bottom:1px solid #242424; scroll-margin-top:88px;\">\n357:   <div class=\"section-inner\">\n358:     <div class=\"section-eyebrow\">What Are Cloud Credits</div>\n359:     <h2 class=\"section-h2\" style=\"max-width:820px;\">Free infrastructure funding the hyperscalers hand to startups. Most founders never claim it.</h2>\n360:     <p class=\"section-p\" style=\"max-width:720px;\"><span class=\"term\" data-term=\"credits\">Cloud credits</span> are grants of <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"compute\">compute</span>, storage and AI capacity, often worth one thousand to one hundred and fifty thousand dollars or more, that Microsoft, AWS and Google give to early stage companies. They let you run servers, databases and GPU workloads for free instead of burning your runway on infrastructure. AKCloud gets you qualified, approved at the highest tier, and builds <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"production\">production</span> systems that run on those credits.</p>\n361:     <div class=\"grid-3\">\n362:       <div style=\"background:#111; border:1px solid #242424; border-radius:8px; padding:30px;\">\n363:         <div style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color:#39FF14; text-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(57,255,20,0.5); margin-bottom:16px;\">&gt; qualify</div>\n364:         <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\">Map the right programs</h3>\n365:         <p style=\"margin:12px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">We match you to Microsoft for Startups, AWS Activate, Google for Startups and F6S, and tell you exactly what each one wants to see to approve you, even pre incorporation.</p>\n366:       </div>\n367:       <div style=\"background:#111; border:1px solid #242424; border-radius:8px; padding:30px;\">\n368:         <div style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color:#39FF14; text-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(57,255,20,0.5); margin-bottom:16px;\">&gt; claim</div>\n369:         <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\">Approved at the top tier</h3>\n370:         <p style=\"margin:12px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">We prepare your application and architecture narrative so you unlock the maximum credit tier, not the entry level grant most founders settle for.</p>\n371:       </div>\n372:       <div style=\"background:#111; border:1px solid #242424; border-radius:8px; padding:30px;\">\n373:         <div style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color:#39FF14; text-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(57,255,20,0.5); margin-bottom:16px;\">&gt; build</div>\n374:         <h3 style=\"margin:0; font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:19px; color:#fff;\">Run <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"production\">production</span> on credits</h3>\n375:         <p style=\"margin:12px 0 0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#C8C8C8;\">We architect compliant, scalable infrastructure that runs on your credit balance, so you launch and grow with near zero cloud spend.</p>\n376:       </div>\n377:     </div>\n378:   </div>\n379: </section>\n380: \n381: <!-- PERKS -->\n382: <section id=\"perks\" style=\"position:relative; z-index:1; max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; box-sizing:border-box; padding:96px 40px; scroll-margin-top:88px;\">\n383:   <div class=\"section-eyebrow\">Perks That Come With Credits</div>\n384:   <h2 class=\"section-h2\" style=\"max-width:760px;\">Credits are the entry point. The programs are where the real leverage is.</h2>\n385:   <div class=\"grid-3\" style=\"margin-top:48px;\">\n386:     <div class=\"perk-card\"><span class=\"perk-dot\"></span><div><div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; color:#fff;\">Up to $150k in credits</div><div style=\"margin-top:6px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#787878;\">Across Azure, AWS and GCP, stacked where the programs allow.</div></div></div>\n387:     <div class=\"perk-card\"><span class=\"perk-dot\"></span><div><div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; color:#fff;\"><span class=\"term\" data-term=\"architecture\">Architecture reviews</span></div><div style=\"margin-top:6px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#787878;\">Free technical support and design reviews from a Microsoft Solutions Partner.</div></div></div>\n388:     <div class=\"perk-card\"><span class=\"perk-dot\"></span><div><div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; color:#fff;\">Investor and <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"f6s\">F6S</span> network</div><div style=\"margin-top:6px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#787878;\">Warm intros and accelerator access through partner ecosystems.</div></div></div>\n389:     <div class=\"perk-card\"><span class=\"perk-dot\"></span><div><div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; color:#fff;\">Discounted tooling</div><div style=\"margin-top:6px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#787878;\">GitHub, OpenAI, <span class=\"term\" data-term=\"datastores\">datastores</span> and dev tools bundled into the programs.</div></div></div>\n390:     <div class=\"perk-card\"><span class=\"perk-dot\"></span><div><div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; color:#fff;\">Co-sell and marketplace</div><div style=\"margin-top:6px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#787878;\">Get listed and co-sold through the hyperscaler marketplaces.</div></div></div>\n391:     <div class=\"perk-card\"><span class=\"perk-dot\"></span><div><div style=\"font-family:'Exo 2',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:16px; color:#fff;\">Mentorship and go-to-market</div><div style=\"margin-top:6px; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; color:#787878;\">Structured guidance from founders who have shipped on the same rails.</div></div></div>\n392:   </div>\n393: </section>\n394: \n395: <!-- CIRCUIT RULE -->\n396: <div class=\"circuit-rule\"><div class=\"circuit-line\"><div class=\"circuit-pulse\" style=\"animation-delay: -2.2s;\"></div></div></div>\n397: \n398: <!-- OUTCOMES -->\n399: <section id=\"stories\" style=\"position:relative; z-index:1; box-sizing:border-box; padding:96px 0; background:#0c0c0c; border-top:1px solid #242424; border-bottom:1px solid #242424; scroll-margin-top:88px;\">\n400:   <div class=\"section-inner\">\n401:     <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:16px;\">\n402:       <div>\n403:         <div class=\"section-eyebrow\">Early Outcomes</div>\n404:         <h2 class=\"section-h2\" style=\"max-width:680px;\">What founders unlock when the credits land.</h2>\n\n(Showing lines 325-404 of 913. Use offset=405 to continue.)\n</content>",
