t-family:\\'JetBrains Mono\\',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:#39FF14;text-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(57,255,20,0.5);margin-bottom:16px;\">&gt; first.run.setup</div>'+\n883:           '<div id=\"_d2ttl\" style=\"font-family:\\'Exo 2\\',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;\">Configure Access</div>'+\n884:           '<div id=\"_d2dsc\" style=\"font-family:\\'DM Sans\\',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#787878;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:22px;\">Set a new identifier and key for this device.</div>'+\n\n(Showing lines 860-884 of 913. Use offset=885 to continue.)\n</content>",
