      "output": "OK: uid=2\r\n\r\nURL/slug fields on appointment.type:\r\n  - website_id                many2one  Restrict to a specific website.\r\n  - website_url               char  The full relative URL to access the document through the website.\r\n  - website_absolute_url      char  The full absolute URL to access the document through the website.\r\n  - website_published         boolean  \r\n  - website_meta_title        char  \r\n  - website_meta_description  text  \r\n  - website_meta_keywords     char  \r\n  - website_meta_og_img       char  \r\n  - website_message_ids       one2many  Website communication history\r\n\r\nRecord #1 — URL / published fields:\r\n  website_id                = False\r\n  website_url               = '/appointment/discovery-consultation-more-1'\r\n  website_absolute_url      = 'https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/appointment/discovery-consultation-more-1'\r\n  website_published         = False\r\n  is_published              = False\r\n  published_date            = False\r\n  website_meta_title        = False\r\n  website_meta_description  = False\r\n  website_meta_keywords     = False\r\n  website_meta_og_img       = False\r\n  website_message_ids       = []\r\n\r\nCandidate public URLs to test:\r\n  https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/appointment/1\r\n  https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/appointment/1-discovery-consultation-and-more\r\n  https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/discovery-consultation-and-more\r\n  https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/book/discovery-consultation-and-more\r\n  https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/page/discovery-consultation-and-more\r\n\r\n",
