ious model — it may live in the URL routing only\r\n\r\n[2] Tour diagnosis\r\n  -- web_tour.tour --\r\n    fields: ['id', 'display_name', 'name', 'step_ids', 'url', 'sharing_url', 'rainbow_man_message', 'sequence', 'custom', 'user_consumed_ids', 'create_uid', 'create_date', 'write_uid', 'write_date']\r\n    record count: 2\r\n    {'id': 16, 'display_name': 'web_studio_new_app_tour', 'name': 'web_studio_new_app_tour', 'step_ids': [], 'url': '/odoo/action-studio?mode=home_menu', 'sharing_url': 'https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/odoo?tour=web_studio_new_app_tour', 'rainbow_man_message': '<span><b>Good job!</b> You went through all steps of this tour.</span>', 'sequence': 1270, 'custom': False, 'user_consumed_ids': [], 'create_uid': [1, 'OdooBot'], 'create_date': '2026-06-23 23:41:54', 'write_uid': [1, 'OdooBot'], 'write_date': '2026-06-23 23:41:54'}\r\n    {'id': 1, 'display_name': 'discuss_channel_tour', 'name': 'discuss_channel_tour', 'step_ids': [], 'url': '/odoo', 'sharing_url': 'https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/odoo?tour=discuss_channel_tour', 'rainbow_man_message': '<span><b>Good job!</b> You went through all steps of this tour.</span>', 'sequence': 2000, 'custom': False, 'user_consumed_ids': [], 'create_uid': [1, 'OdooBot'], 'create_date': '2026-06-23 23:29:03', 'write_uid': [1, 'OdooBot'], 'write_date': '2026-06-23 23:29:03'}\r\n  - model tour.tracker: not present\r\n  - model tour: not present\r\n\r\n[3] res.users fields related to tour\r\n  tour-related fields: ['tour_enabled']\r\n  me: {'id': 2, 'name': 'AndieKobbiePics, Andrea Enning', 'login': 'andiekobbietks@outlook.com', 'tour_enabled': True}\r\n\r\n[4] appointment.type #1 — full schema + current values\r\n  name='Discovery Consultation & More'  duration=0.75min  published=False\r\n  min_hours=1.0  max_days=14\r\n  has_intro_html=False  has_invite_html=False\r\n  host_user_id=None  location=AndieKobbieTech, City Campus, Usk Way, Newport NP20 2BP\r\n  message_confirmation: False\r\n\r\n  Total schema fields: 105\r\n    appointment_duration                float\r\n    appointment_duration_formatted      char\r\n    appointment_invite_count            integer\r\n    appointment_invite_ids              many2many\r\n    auto_confirm                        boolean\r\n    has_message                         boolean\r\n    hide_duration                       boolean\r\n    image_1024                          binary\r\n    image_128                           binary\r\n    image_1920                          binary\r\n    image_256                           binary\r\n    image_512                           binary\r\n    is_always_confirm                   boolean\r\n    location                            char\r\n    location_id                         many2one\r\n    manual_confirmation_percentage      float\r\n    message_attachment_count            integer\r\n    message_confirmation                html\r\n    message_follower_ids                one2many\r\n    message_has_error                   boolean\r\n    message_has_error_counter           integer\r\n    message_has_sms_error               boolean\r\n    message_ids                         one2many\r\n    message_intro                       html\r\n    message_is_follower                 boolean\r\n    message_needaction                  boolean\r\n    message_needaction_counter          integer\r\n    message_partner_ids                 many2many\r\n    show_avatars                        boolean\r\n    website_absolute_url                char\r\n    website_message_ids                 one2many\r\n    website_url                         char\r\n\r\n",
