      "text": "Now I have the full picture. The tour is a `web_tour.tour` with empty `step_ids`, and your `res.users.tour_enabled = True` is what's making the backend try to resume it on every page load. Appointment type is intact and customizable. Let me fix the tour and make the page Calendly-like in one go.",
