      "tool": "bash",
      "code": "{\"command\": \"$r = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \\\"https://andiekobbie.odoo.com/book/27e80afd\\\" -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 20\\n$h = $r.Content\\nWrite-Host \\\"=== title ===\\\"; (Select-String -InputObject $h -Pattern \\\"<title>[^<]*</title>\\\" -AllMatches).Matches[0].Value\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== heading(s) ===\\\"; (Select-String -InputObject $h -Pattern \\\"<h[12][^>]*>[^<]+</h[12]>\\\" -AllMatches).Matches | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== looking for our intro markers ===\\\"\\n$markers = @(\\\"Discovery Consultation\\\",\\\"Sovereign cloud journey\\\",\\\"Exo 2\\\",\\\"Video call\\\",\\\"30 minutes\\\",\\\"30 mins\\\",\\\"45 mins\\\",\\\"AndieKobbieTech\\\",\\\"City Campus\\\",\\\"Usk Way\\\",\\\"NP20 2BP\\\",\\\"Andrea\\\")\\nforeach ($m in $markers) {\\n  $cnt = ([regex]::Matches($h, [regex]::Escape($m))).Count\\n  if ($cnt -gt 0) { Write-Host \\\"  $cnt \\u00d7 $m\\\" } else { Write-Host \\\"  ---  $m (absent)\\\" }\\n}\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== confirmation message check ===\\\"\\n$markers2 = @(\\\"You're booked\\\",\\\"calendar invite\\\",\\\"AKCloud\\\",\\\"Andrea @ AKCloud\\\",\\\"Good job!\\\",\\\"web_studio_new_app_tour\\\")\\nforeach ($m in $markers2) {\\n  $cnt = ([regex]::Matches($h, [regex]::Escape($m))).Count\\n  if ($cnt -gt 0) { Write-Host \\\"  $cnt \\u00d7 $m\\\" } else { Write-Host \\\"  ---  $m (absent)\\\" }\\n}\", \"timeout\": 30000, \"description\": \"Inspect what's actually rendered on the share link page\"}",
      "output": "=== title ===\n<title>Discovery Consultation &amp; More | AndieKobbie</title>\r\n\n=== heading(s) ===\n<h1 class=\"d-none d-md-block mb-4 h4\">Discovery Consultation &amp; More</h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"font-family:'Exo 2', sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:22px; color:#0f172a; margin:0 0 8px;\">Discovery Consultation</h2>\r\n\n=== looking for our intro markers ===\n  5 � Discovery Consultation\n  ---  Sovereign cloud journey (absent)\n  1 � Exo 2\n  1 � Video call\n  3 � 30 minutes\n  ---  30 mins (absent)\n  ---  45 mins (absent)\n  1 � AndieKobbieTech\n  1 � City Campus\n  1 � Usk Way\n  1 � NP20 2BP\n  ---  Andrea (absent)\n\n=== confirmation message check ===\n  ---  You're booked (absent)\n  ---  calendar invite (absent)\n  ---  AKCloud (absent)\n  ---  Andrea @ AKCloud (absent)\n  ---  Good job! (absent)\n  ---  web_studio_new_app_tour (absent)\n",
