      "output": "OK: uid=2\r\n\r\n[1] Fetch the assets bundle — see if it loads at all\r\n  /web/assets/1902c8e/web.assets_web.min.js\r\n     status=200  bytes=7481879  type=application/javascript; charset=utf-8\r\n     head: b'\\n/* /web/static/src/module_loader.js */\\n(function(odoo){\"use strict\";if(odoo.loader){return;}\\nclass ModuleLoader{bus=new EventTarget();checkErrorProm=null;factories=new Map();failed=new Set();jobs=new'\r\n  /web/assets/598b577/web.assets_web.min.css\r\n     status=200  bytes=1206695  type=text/css; charset=utf-8\r\n     head: b'\\n/* <inline asset> */\\n@charset \"UTF-8\"; \\n\\n/* /web/static/lib/bootstrap/scss/_functions.scss */\\n \\n\\n/* /web/static/lib/bootstrap/scss/_mixins.scss */\\n \\n\\n/* /web/static/src/scss/functions.scss */\\n \\n\\n/* /'\r\n\r\n[2] ir.attachment — assets bundle cache\r\n  9 matching attachments:\r\n    [1250] web.assets_frontend_lazy.min.js                          type=binary   size=   2311150  wrote=2026-06-24 05:07:01\r\n    [1249] web.assets_frontend.min.css                              type=binary   size=    876099  wrote=2026-06-24 05:07:00\r\n    [1248] web.assets_backend_lazy.min.css                          type=binary   size=    154190  wrote=2026-06-24 00:43:54\r\n    [1247] web.assets_backend_lazy.min.js                           type=binary   size=    585916  wrote=2026-06-24 00:43:54\r\n    [1246] web.assets_web_print.min.css                             type=binary   size=   1212178  wrote=2026-06-24 00:43:13\r\n    [1245] web.assets_web.min.js                                    type=binary   size=   7481879  wrote=2026-06-24 00:43:12\r\n    [1244] web.assets_web.min.css                                   type=binary   size=   1206695  wrote=2026-06-24 00:43:12\r\n    [1203] web.assets_frontend_minimal.min.js                       type=binary   size=     34659  wrote=2026-06-23 23:41:05\r\n    [1200] web.assets_emoji.min.js                                  type=binary   size=    458331  wrote=2026-06-23 23:30:09\r\n\r\n[3] ir.qweb fields + asset bundles\r\n  ir.qweb fields: ['id', 'display_name']\r\n  ERR: <Fault 4: \"You are not allowed to access 'Qweb' (ir.qweb) records.\\n\\nNo group currently allows this operation.\\n\\nContact your administrator to request access if necessary.\">\r\n\r\n[4] Hunt for 'regenerate' / 'clear' / 'invalidate' methods on common models\r\n\r\n[5] Find + (preview-only, not delete yet) the assets cache entries\r\n  matched 9 web.assets attachments\r\n  ir.attachment name field exists: True\r\n\r\n[6] Registry hash + view/asset health\r\n  current registry_hash: d99bd19cbe554b1006cffef8ebd7511d55753b79cb74b6e297f66b07eb3bd906\r\n  active ir.ui.view count: 1778\r\n\r\n",
