      "text": "The assets bundle is loading (7.4MB JS, status 200), and the registry hash hasn't changed — so Odoo thinks everything's fine. But the bundle was compiled right at the moment of the module uninstall (00:43:12), which is exactly when things can go sideways. Let me force a clean recompile by nuking the stale backend assets cache.",
