      "output": "OK: uid=2\r\n\r\n[1] Find a good home action to set on the user\r\n  base.open_menu -> #1\r\n\r\n  Settings action:\r\n\r\n[2] Look up a known-good action to use as a landing target\r\n  using home_action_id = False\r\n\r\n[3] Verify public appointment page (case-insensitive markers)\r\n  /book/27e80afd  status=200  bytes=138410\r\n     OK   title 'Discovery Consultation & More'\r\n     OK   h1 'Discovery Consultation & More'\r\n     --   title 'Discovery Consultation' (new)\r\n     OK   h2 'Discovery Consultation' (new)\r\n     OK   intro: 'sovereign cloud journey'\r\n     OK   pill: 'video call'\r\n     OK   pill: '30 minutes'\r\n     OK   pill: 'europe/london'\r\n     OK   pill: 'free'\r\n     --   host: 'andrea'\r\n  tour markers in HTML: 0 (should be 0)\r\n\r\n[4] Verify canonical /appointment/<slug> URL\r\n  /appointment/discovery-consultation-1  status=200  bytes=138335\r\n     title matches 'Discovery Consultation' (new): False\r\n     title matches 'Discovery Consultation & More' (old): True\r\n     has 'sovereign cloud journey' intro: True\r\n\r\n[5] Backend status\r\n  /odoo (unauth) status=200 bytes=23075  is_login=True  is_spa_shell=False\r\n  → when the user refreshes /odoo in their browser, Odoo will recompile\r\n     the deleted backend assets and serve fresh JS+CSS.\r\n\r\n",
